  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Girls' Kitchen Diner</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278120/extras/c5ea152dfd064a3bc3753f3b9ad2b083.poster.avif?t=1743423005\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278120/extras/c5ea152dfd064a3bc3753f3b9ad2b083.webm?t=1743423005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278120/extras/c5ea152dfd064a3bc3753f3b9ad2b083.mp4?t=1743423005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Girls' Kitchen Diner is a vibrant cooking game full of personality, where a group of skilled women runs a restaurant their way. Among scattered ingredients, stoves catching fire, and demanding customers, the characters face daily challenges while balancing work, friendship, and unexpected romantic moments. With an engaging mix of comedy and chaos, the restaurant becomes the perfect stage to show that talent, care, and a pinch of madness are the main ingredients for success – and maybe even for love. 🍔🍟🍕🌭</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278120/extras/da9b60be8d377b50c0d85f0821472025.poster.avif?t=1743423005\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278120/extras/da9b60be8d377b50c0d85f0821472025.webm?t=1743423005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278120/extras/da9b60be8d377b50c0d85f0821472025.mp4?t=1743423005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >OLIVIA 🍏</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BIANCA 🍋</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CAROL 🍑</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >LIZ 🍇</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >THE CRITIC 🍒</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The playable characters in Girls' Kitchen Diner are talented and charismatic women, each with unique cooking skills and striking personalities. The datable characters bring an extra dose of charm and fun to the story, with relationships developing unexpectedly, adding romance and many twists to the culinary chaos. 🥪🌮🌯🥙</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278120/extras/8d022febe1a2c83e4bb739c5258301ad.poster.avif?t=1743423005\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278120/extras/8d022febe1a2c83e4bb739c5258301ad.webm?t=1743423005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278120/extras/8d022febe1a2c83e4bb739c5258301ad.mp4?t=1743423005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Girls' Kitchen Diner</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278120/extras/c5ea152dfd064a3bc3753f3b9ad2b083.poster.avif?t=1743423005\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278120/extras/c5ea152dfd064a3bc3753f3b9ad2b083.webm?t=1743423005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278120/extras/c5ea152dfd064a3bc3753f3b9ad2b083.mp4?t=1743423005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Girls' Kitchen Diner is a vibrant cooking game full of personality, where a group of skilled women runs a restaurant their way. Among scattered ingredients, stoves catching fire, and demanding customers, the characters face daily challenges while balancing work, friendship, and unexpected romantic moments. With an engaging mix of comedy and chaos, the restaurant becomes the perfect stage to show that talent, care, and a pinch of madness are the main ingredients for success – and maybe even for love. 🍔🍟🍕🌭</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278120/extras/da9b60be8d377b50c0d85f0821472025.poster.avif?t=1743423005\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278120/extras/da9b60be8d377b50c0d85f0821472025.webm?t=1743423005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278120/extras/da9b60be8d377b50c0d85f0821472025.mp4?t=1743423005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >OLIVIA 🍏</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BIANCA 🍋</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CAROL 🍑</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >LIZ 🍇</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >THE CRITIC 🍒</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The playable characters in Girls' Kitchen Diner are talented and charismatic women, each with unique cooking skills and striking personalities. The datable characters bring an extra dose of charm and fun to the story, with relationships developing unexpectedly, adding romance and many twists to the culinary chaos. 🥪🌮🌯🥙</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278120/extras/8d022febe1a2c83e4bb739c5258301ad.poster.avif?t=1743423005\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278120/extras/8d022febe1a2c83e4bb739c5258301ad.webm?t=1743423005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278120/extras/8d022febe1a2c83e4bb739c5258301ad.mp4?t=1743423005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
